# 🛒 MSN Mart

> **A Modern Full-Stack E-Commerce Web Application built with Spring Boot, Thymeleaf, Spring Security, Razorpay, Twilio, and MySQL.**

MSN Mart is a secure and scalable e-commerce platform that provides a complete online shopping experience. The application follows a layered architecture and integrates enterprise-grade features such as authentication, role-based authorization, online payment processing, OTP verification, email notifications, and responsive UI design.

---

## 🚀 Features

### 👤 Authentication & Security

* User Registration & Login
* Spring Security Authentication
* Role-Based Authorization (Admin & Customer)
* BCrypt Password Encryption
* OTP Verification
* Password Reset via Email
* Session Management

