## 🏗️ Project Architecture

```
Presentation Layer
        │
        ▼
Controller Layer
        │
        ▼
Service Layer
(Business Logic)
        │
        ▼
Repository Layer
(Spring Data JPA)
        │
        ▼
MySQL Database
```

The project follows the **Layered Architecture Pattern**, making the code modular, maintainable, and easy to scale.

